OL,3,CGuernsey Electricity could pay #100
OL,4,Cmillion for undersea link to France
OL,6,FA new underwater cable from Guernsey
OL,7,Fto France is closer to reality, ITV
OL,8,FNews understands.
OL,10,FThe move would increase energy
OL,11,Fsecurity and give the island direct
OL,12,Faccess to green energy from the
OL,13,FEuropean grid.
OL,15,FThe idea has been mooted for several
OL,16,Fyears, as Guernsey currently relies on
OL,17,Fa single undersea link from Jersey,
OL,18,Fwhich itself is connected to France
OL,19,Fwith three underwater cables.
