OL,3,CGuernsey Electricity could pay #100
OL,4,Cmillion for undersea link to France
OL,6,FGuernsey's demand for electricity can
OL,7,Foutstrip capacity on the Jersey line,
OL,8,Fmeaning the island's power station is
OL,9,Fsometimes used to fill the gaps.
OL,11,FHowever, it is seen as an expensive
OL,12,Flast resort that Guernsey Electricity
OL,13,Fare keen to move away from in favour
OL,14,Fof low-carbon sources - France uses
OL,15,Fnuclear power for around 70% of its
OL,16,Felectricity.
