OL,3,CGuernsey Electricity could pay #100
OL,4,Cmillion for undersea link to France
OL,6,FA direct link to France would mean the
OL,7,Fpower station is no longer needed and
OL,8,Fdespite already spending #30 million
OL,9,Fon replacing the current Jersey-
OL,10,FGuernsey undersea cable, Guernsey
OL,11,FElectricity still believes an extra
OL,12,Fconnection will be worth it in the
OL,13,Flong run.
