OL,3,CGuernsey Electricity could pay #100
OL,4,Cmillion for undersea link to France
OL,6,FJon Sexton, Head of Generation at the
OL,7,Futility company, explains: "Our
OL,8,Fchallenge is to increase the security
OL,9,Fof that inter-connection route, which
OL,10,Fhas given us huge access to low-carbon
OL,11,Felectricity from the European grid
OL,12,Fsince 2000 and helped to maintain our
OL,13,Fprice stability since.
OL,15,F"But we've only got one of them, so we
OL,16,Fneed to increase the capacity that
OL,17,Fcomes into Guernsey and having two
OL,18,Finterconnectors increases our
OL,19,Fresilience, which is key for our
OL,20,Fcustomers."
