OL,3,CGuernsey Electricity could pay #100
OL,4,Cmillion for undersea link to France
OL,6,FIn its 'strategic vision' for the next
OL,7,Fdecade, Guernsey Electricity says it
OL,8,Faims to build a direct cable to Europe
OL,9,For to improve its current connection
OL,10,Fto Jersey.
OL,12,FA decision is expected early next year
OL,13,Fand either choice would come at a
OL,14,Fsignificant cost, with the utility
OL,15,Fcompany predicting to spend around
OL,16,F#100 million on subsea cables.
OL,18,FDespite some proposed borrowing,
OL,19,Fislanders would also be expected to
OL,20,Ffoot some of the bill.
