OL,3,CGuernsey Electricity could pay #100
OL,4,Cmillion for undersea link to France
OL,6,FThe extent of any tariff rises is
OL,7,Funclear, but they are likely to affect
OL,8,Fall customers, given that fixed price
OL,9,Fcontracts are set to end in 2027.
OL,11,FThe island's power station is also
OL,12,Fageing, with some of the site's
OL,13,Fequipment half a century old and in
OL,14,Fneed of continuing maintenance.
